org.activity.distances

Class FeatureWiseWeightedEditDistance

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.activity.distances.AlignmentBasedDistance
      • org.activity.distances.FeatureWiseWeightedEditDistance

  • public class FeatureWiseWeightedEditDistance
extends AlignmentBasedDistance
    It is a featurewise weighted edit distance. The edit operations are weighted. The edit distance is an aggregation of weighted edit distances between the corresponding symbolic representation of the feature timelines.
    Author:
    gunjan
